{"ts":"2026-05-10T19:58:16.192Z","type":"response","data":{"response":"A fair question, sir — Agent has consulted the vault on your behalf.\n\nIt appears the results returned empty, which suggests either your task list is currently bare, or the vault seed does not yet contain any task entries.\n\nWhat Agent *can* tell you from the current context is this:\n\n- **Overdue tasks:** 1\n- **Due today:** 0\n- **Due tomorrow:** 0\n\nThere is at least one overdue task lurking about, though the details weren't surfaced in this pass. Shall Agent dig deeper and retrieve the specifics of that overdue item? I'd be most happy to pull it up and, if you like, reschedule or action it straightaway."}}
{"ts":"2026-05-10T19:58:16.195Z","type":"summary","data":{"inputTokens":11877,"outputTokens":1098,"totalTokens":12975,"estimatedCostUsd":0.028959,"calls":[{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","inputTokens":129,"outputTokens":74,"costUsd":0.0003992,"prompt":{"system":"You are an intent classifier for a personal assistant. Available entity types: person, business, task, event, note. Return JSON only.","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"User said: \"what tasks do I have?\"\nReturn JSON only:\n{\n  \"summary\": \"one sentence describing what the user wants\",\n  \"actionType\": \"query|create|update|delete|mixed\",\n  \"entityTypes\": [\"task\"],\n  \"timeframe\": \"past|present|future|range|any\",\n  \"isSimple\": true,\n  \"confidence\": 0.9\n}"}]},"response":"```json\n{\n  \"summary\": \"The user wants to retrieve a list of their current tasks.\",\n  \"actionType\": \"query\",\n  \"entityTypes\": [\"task\"],\n  \"timeframe\": \"present\",\n  \"isSimple\": true,\n  \"confidence\": 0.95\n}\n```"},{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","inputTokens":1231,"outputTokens":128,"costUsd":0.0014968000000000002,"prompt":{"system":"You are a context gathering agent for a personal assistant. Fetch only the entities needed to understand the user's situation. Return JSON only.","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Intent: The user wants to retrieve a list of their current tasks.\nAction type: query\n\nAvailable context (manifest):\n{\n  \"entityTypes\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"task\",\n      \"plural\": \"tasks\",\n      \"count\": 3,\n      \"description\": \"Things to do\",\n      \"fields\": [\n        \"status\",\n        \"priority\",\n        \"dueDate\"\n      ],\n      \"dateRange\": {\n        \"earliest\": \"2026-05-01\",\n        \"latest\": \"2026-05-14\"\n      },\n      \"recentSamples\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"book-dentist\",\n          \"title\": \"Book dentist appointment\",\n          \"tags\": [\n            \"task\",\n            \"personal\",\